description: "This library is a Microsoft effort to support cloud-based client-server communication in native code using a modern asynchronous C++ API design. The C++ REST SDK is a project to start exploring how to best support C++ developers who want to take advantage of the radical shift in software architecture that cloud computing represents."
summary: "The C++ REST SDK is a cross-platform, modern, and asynchronous library that enables developers to access and author connected applications"
title: C++ REST SDK
